short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provides support for annotating HTML websites with Brandshare Collaboration

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Brandshare collaboration (brandshareco.co) Allows users to annotate different types of files.
This extension allows Brandshare collaboration users to annotate websites with Brandshare Collaboration(brandshareco.co).

* This extension only works with brandshareco.co specific subdomains (ex: https://dev.brandshareco.co)
